        <abstract> 
<p>Believes AG’s cases of incipient dimorphism are due to mere variability. Has found examples in <hi rend="italic">Nolana</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Amsinckia</hi>; believes such variation is the basis for the development of dimorphism. Was unaware of variations in <hi rend="italic">Phlox</hi>.</p>  
<p>Sensitivity of <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Dionaea</hi>.</p> 
