            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 11, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4053.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Asa Gray, 20 March [1863]</ref> and n. 19; CD refers to <hi rend="italic">Amsinckia spectabilis</hi>.</note>
